Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因偶然認識的一位名叫戴安娜的英國女子的邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.31,0:00:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們啟程前往英國
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.87,0:00:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然用江戶川柯南的身份是無法出國的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.84,0:00:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我利用從灰原那裡得到的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.67,0:00:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時恢復成了工藤新一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.05,0:01:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻沒想到在我去英國的這段時間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會發生那樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是借住在吉田同學家呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.36,0:01:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我的房間真是大不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.89,0:01:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哀 你醒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸媽媽突然有急事 出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽做了三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.78,0:02:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 起床了 去洗臉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.69,0:02:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也按計劃行動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.85,0:02:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐可真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.13,0:02:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能理整齊了再拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都要別人來弄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grays Aihara
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.06,0:03:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人真像灰原
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.22,0:03:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 有電話找你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.81,0:03:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是柯南打來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很急的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是光彥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天千萬不要讓灰原靠近博士家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.11,0:03:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以跟她在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.67,0:03:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫忙看緊她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.83,0:03:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂…喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓灰原靠近博士家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是為什麼呢
